CSL_Language :: Enum
      I. Valid tests:
           - enum_ei_eq_ei.pl => generates valid tests for enum with verilog numbers
           - enum_verilog_valid_gen.pl => generates valid tests for enum
     II.Invalid tests:
           - enum_no_char_float_invalid.pl =>generates invalid tests for enum with verilog number
           - enum_verilog_invalid_gen.pl => generates invalid tests  for enum

